article.headline: Robinson scores 20 as Little Rock downs Southern Indiana 77-75
article.description: — Khalen Robinson scored 20 points as Little Rock beat Southern Indiana 77-75 on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Robinson scores 20 as Little Rock downs Southern Indiana 77-75
article.story: EVANSVILLE, Ind. -- — Khalen Robinson scored 20 points as Little Rock beat Southern Indiana 77-75 on Thursday night. Robinson also had 12 rebounds and seven assists for the Trojans (9-10, 3-3 Ohio Valley Conference). Jordan Jefferson was 3-of-5 shooting and 4 of 5 from the free-throw line to add 12 points. Jamir Chaplin had 10 points and shot 5 for 12 (0 for 5 from 3-point range) and 0 of 3 from the free-throw line. Jeremiah Hernandez led the way for the Screaming Eagles (5-14, 2-4) with 28 points and three steals. Southern Indiana also got 17 points from Jack Mielke. Javius Moore also put up 15 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
